(3204, 4, '2015-04-13 22:19:04', '2015-04-13 22:19:04', '[vc_row layout=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias=\"one-page-slider\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1428882355299{padding-top: 85px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}\" section_id=\"about-us\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>The Flexible Capital Fund, L3C (Flex Fund) provides creative financing in the form of near equity capital (<a href=\"/investments/\">subordinated debt and royalty financing</a>) to Vermonts growth-stage companies in sustainable agriculture and food systems, forest products, and clean technology sectors. As the only licensed lender in Vermont to provide royalty financing, the <a href=\"/who-we-are/\">Flex Fund</a> invests in Vermont companies that strengthen or fill a gap in their supply chain. The Flex Fund is a <strong>Community Development Financial Institution</strong> (CDFI) lender, which provides advisory and development resources to help <a href=\"/portfolio/\">portfolio companies</a> grow.</h4>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section_id=\"about-us\" css=\".vc_custom_1468270626891{padding-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<a href=\"/who-we-are/\">Learn more</a> about where the Flex Fund (and other organizations that provide funding) fit along Vermonts capital continuum.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_button title=\"Download Vermonts Capital Continuum\" color=\"custom\" custom_color=\"#8bc63f\" custom_border_color=\"#8bc63f\" icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-download\" href=\"http://flexiblecapitalfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Flex-Fund-Vermont-Capital-Continuum.pdf\" add_icon=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1468173795134{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;background-color: #222222 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">\"We are committed to helping our portfolio companies grow and stay in Vermont so they can create quality jobs and sustainable products and services. Ultimately, our aim is to support the businesses that can accelerate the rate at which we move towards healthy food systems, renewable energy, and climate change solutions.\"</span></h2>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #cccccc;\"><em> Janice St. Onge, Flex Fund President</em></span></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1468346222867{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"3232\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" onclick=\"custom_link\" css_animation=\"bottom-to-top\" link=\"/who-we-are/\"][vc_separator style=\"blank\" padding_top=\"10\" padding_bottom=\"10\"][ctitle title=\"Background\" color=\"#232323\" background=\"#ffffff\" font_size=\"20\" font_weight=\"600\" position=\"left\" separator_color=\"rgba(235,235,235,0.01)\"][vc_column_text]The Flexible Capital Fund, L3C (Flex Fund) is a low profit, limited liability company launched in 2011 by the Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund, a non-profit organization whose mission is to accelerate Vermonts green economy.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Learn More\" color=\"custom\" custom_color=\"#8bc63f\" custom_border_color=\"#8bc63f\" i_align=\"right_icon\" icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-arrow-right\" align=\"left\" href=\"/who-we-are/\" add_icon=\"true\" full_width=\"true\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"3234\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" onclick=\"custom_link\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" link=\"/financing/\"][vc_separator style=\"blank\" padding_top=\"10\" padding_bottom=\"10\"][ctitle title=\"Financing\" color=\"#232323\" background=\"#ffffff\" font_size=\"20\" font_weight=\"600\" position=\"left\" separator_color=\"rgba(235,235,235,0.01)\"][vc_column_text]The Flexible Capital Fund (Flex Fund) offers Vermont growth-stage companies in sustainable agriculture and food systems, forest products, and clean technology sectors.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Learn More\" color=\"custom\" custom_color=\"#8bc63f\" custom_border_color=\"#8bc63f\" i_align=\"right_icon\" icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-arrow-right\" align=\"left\" href=\"/financing/\" add_icon=\"true\" full_width=\"true\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"3372\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" onclick=\"custom_link\" css_animation=\"bottom-to-top\" link=\"/portfolio/\"][vc_separator style=\"blank\" padding_top=\"10\" padding_bottom=\"10\"][ctitle title=\"Portfolio\" color=\"#232323\" background=\"#ffffff\" font_size=\"20\" font_weight=\"600\" position=\"left\" separator_color=\"rgba(235,235,235,0.01)\"][vc_column_text]The Flex Fund investments support portfolio companies which will strengthen their existing markets across the value chain  now and for future generations.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Learn More\" color=\"custom\" custom_color=\"#8bc63f\" custom_border_color=\"#8bc63f\" i_align=\"right_icon\" icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-arrow-right\" align=\"left\" href=\"/portfolio/\" add_icon=\"true\" full_width=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section_id=\"blog\" css=\".vc_custom_1468345300216{padding-top: 30px !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"News &amp; Press\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:24|text_align:center|color:%23333333|line_height:1.5\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Arvo%3Aregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\" link=\"url:%23||\"][vc_separator_2 color_line=\"#333333\" padding_top=\"20\" padding_bottom=\"55\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section_id=\"blog\" css=\".vc_custom_1468345268152{padding-bottom: 80px !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][recent_posts columns=\"3\" show_date=\"no\" taxonomies=