(3503, 2, '2017-06-05 14:12:59', '2017-06-05 18:12:59', 'Common Good Vermont interviews Janice St. Onge, the Deputy Director, Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund, Inc. and President of the VSJF Flexible Capital Fund, L3C. Janice discusses the importance of capital for Vermont\'s innovative businesses, how the Flexible Capital Fund has secured resources to benefit the state, how it works for businesses seeking capital, and the challenges and opportunities companies and mission-driven organizations face when trying to grow their businesses.\n\n[su_button url=\"<a href=\"https://www.cctv.org/watch-tv/programs/opportunities-and-challenges-capitalization-growth-janice-st-onge\">http://www.vsjf.org/what-we-do/flexible-capital-fund/In-the-News</a>\" target=\"blank\" background=\"#8bc63f\" radius=\"0\"]Watch on CCTV.org[/su_button]', 'Common Good Vermont: Opportunities and Challenges in Capitalization & Growth', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1605-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-06-05 14:12:59', '2017-06-05 18:12:59', '', 1605, 'http://flexiblecapitalfund.com/1605-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
